=E2=80=9CWe owned some luna,=E2=80=9D Mr Carnegie said from Singapore, wher=
e he lives. =E2=80=9CWe net ended up square or maybe down a bit. With a Pon=
zi scheme you are trying to get in and out early.=E2=80=9D ...
