<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CEveryone who should be using the tech=
nology isn=E2=80=99t because they hate the crypto bros. Quite rightly they =
should hate them because they are such scumbags.=E2=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">He said Mr Kwon and other crypto entrepreneurs=
 operating stablecoins were engaged in a form of banking where their financ=
ial reserves could not cover, at any one time, their liabilities.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CThey have no view of history and no h=
istorical context,=E2=80=9D he said. =E2=80=9CThey feel they are discoverin=
g everything for the first time. It was leveraged fractional banking, which=
 has been run a gazillion times again and again.=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">See I would quibble that what Terra actually r=
ediscovered was <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/29=
