coration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #=
000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">death-spiral f=
inancing</a>, not leveraged banking, but I agree with the general sentiment=
. If you come to crypto because (1) you are very self-confident=C2=A0and (2=
) you don=E2=80=99t know anything about traditional finance and don=E2=80=
=99t want to find out, then you will have a lot of fun repeating and magnif=
ying the historical errors of traditional finance.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Also: =E2=80=9CWith a Ponzi scheme you are try=
ing to get in and out early=E2=80=9D! A reasonable trading approach.=C2=A0A=
 problem in <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/291249=
